{"tid":1937633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報胡錫進轟廣東：應隔離港澳台入境人士","createTime":"2020-03-22T05:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T06:00:05.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"392309c3a192e20a1e481628c15e139fe6d8b4d9","tid":1937633,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"胡錫進微博原文：<br />\n<br />\n廣東省的這個新規是什麼意思？是港澳台入粵人員可以不隔離嗎？如果是這樣，老胡作為內地媒體人表示反對。<br />\n<br />\n港澳台與內地是不同的抗疫管理體系，有不同的檢測標準，港台近日病例激增，形勢尤其危險，決不能對從那裡進入內地的人網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n那樣將使剛剛本土新增病例歸零的內地面臨第二次感染的巨大風險。呼籲廣東省重新考慮這個政策，大疫當前，內地的安全第一，其他都應排在之後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2597126/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E8%BD%9F%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%EF%BC%9A%E6%87%89%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2597126%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=e7acebcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2597126/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E8%BD%9F%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%EF%BC%9A%E6%87%89%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB</a>"},{"pid":"0b7fe7fdd8ce598d7b0c3fae85946f0687db1f21","tid":1937633,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"點解咁鐘意自稱老胡"},{"pid":"d99169b9e2f27fa1bbbba72